-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Encoding ASCII text.

< data Bit = O | I
<  deriving (Show, Eq, Ord)

< encode ∷ (Eq char) ⇒ Tree char → [char] → [Bit]

< codes ∷ Tree char → [(char, [Bit])]

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Decoding a Huffman binary.

< decode ∷ Tree char → [Bit] → [char]

